3
00:00:12,654 --> 00:00:15,829
We'll talk about the challenges
these systems face,

4
00:00:15,829 --> 00:00:20,621
and how to address these challenges
in the context of sustainability.

5
00:00:21,005 --> 00:00:23,785
Sustainability is particularly
relevant here,

6
00:00:23,785 --> 00:00:28,831
because all the energy problems of cities
pertain to sustainability.

7
00:00:29,741 --> 00:00:32,701
This block is structured
into five sessions.

8
00:00:33,152 --> 00:00:36,506
In the first session, we will broadly talk

9
00:00:36,506 --> 00:00:40,000
about the relationship
between energy and cities.

10
00:00:40,408 --> 00:00:44,223
From there, we will focus
in particular on electricity.

11
00:00:44,223 --> 00:00:47,684
First, we will understand
the electricity system,

12
00:00:47,684 --> 00:00:49,372
in the second session,

13
00:00:49,372 --> 00:00:51,648
and in the third session we will then see

14
00:00:51,648 --> 00:00:54,806
